data.description: Opportunity knocks…why rent when you can own?  Welcome to 335 Walnut Street!  This lovely 2 story well maintained home has a gracious entry and smooth transition into the kitchen, a pleasant flow for entertaining guests. As you make your way up the open staircase to the 2nd floor you will find 3 bedrooms with closets and a full bath. Making your way back down the stairs and into the kitchen you can exit to the outdoor entertaining patio, ample rear yard and your own off-street parking (3 cars spaces). The basement houses the mechanicals for the home, washer/dryer and is accessed from the kitchen hallway as well as the Bilco door access to and from the backyard.  This property is walking distance to all the downtown shops, restaurants, breweries/bars that Pottstown has to offer!  Make an appointment and come see yourself calling this HOME!
